      "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A psychiatrist is discussing drug dependence with a group of medical students. Which of the following statements regarding drug dependence is NOT typically included in its definition?</span></span></p>",
